---
title: Caldereta-Style Ground Turkey with Peppers, Peas and Rice
description: We've quickened up this traditional Filipino tomato-based stew by using minced turkey! Full of peppers, peas, garlic and a hint of soy, this hearty stew is a perfect family dinner.
